  "intro": "<p>\n</p><p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &amp;quote;Helvetica Neue&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;PingFang SC&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quote;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当太阳升起的时候，我将生命绽放成一朵太阳花，永远追逐着光明、温暖、美好。</p>\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &amp;quote;Helvetica Neue&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;PingFang SC&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quote;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"> </p>\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &amp;quote;Helvetica Neue&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;PingFang SC&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quote;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">当月亮升起的时候，我是一株暗夜里的丁香，清凉、淡漠、幽香……修行者的旅途不舍昼夜。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &amp;quote;Helvetica Neue&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;PingFang SC&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quote;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">节选--（佛说：“如果有宿世习气业种，一时不能断除，你可教这个人，一心持诵我的佛顶光明、摩诃萨怛多，般怛啰无上神咒。摩诃萨怛多，般怛啰(楞严咒)，译作大白伞盖。如能一心持念至功夫深时，则数千里内，都可平安无事，可令大事化小，小事化无……）<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &amp;quote;Helvetica Neue&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;PingFang SC&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quote;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">桑吉平措一曲《大白伞盖佛母心咒》又像是在你生命中盛开的一朵“五瓣丁香”，那是芬芳的幸运之花。或许就是佛母庇佑的天使，从天外飞来，守护着你日日夜夜。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n        </p>\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &amp;quote;Helvetica Neue&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;PingFang SC&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quote;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n近期，首部佛陀经教电影《首楞严演义》将上映，桑吉平措发布《大白伞盖佛母心咒》，这首梵歌也是他作为主演的第一部电影而献礼。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n</p>\n<p style=\"max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: -apple-system-font, &amp;quote;Helvetica Neue&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;PingFang SC&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Hiragino Sans GB&amp;quote;, &amp;quote;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quote;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“嗡玛玛吽尼娑哈” 是美丽的语言，充满了温暖和圣洁的大爱，桑吉平措希望这美好的世界充满着祝福和问候，也是祝愿这世间和世间的生灵都平和安好，纯洁美善。<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n春是开始，丁香绽放的此刻，让我们一同随桑吉平措进入那美丽的芬芳。。。</p>\n<p></p>",
